	<h3>NARA and NHPRC</h3><a href="http://www.archives.gov/grants/about_nhprc/strategic_plan.html">NARA | NHPRC and Other Grants | Strategic Plan</a>.&nbsp; How NHPRC operates, including mission, identification of stakeholders, and how they intend to proceed and perform.<br>
