	<a href="http://www.archives.gov/grants/about_nhprc/about_nhprc.html">NARA | NHPRC and Other Grants | About NHPRC</a>.&nbsp; eGovernment is a wonderful thing.&nbsp; What did the fellow say" "Show me the money?"&nbsp; Here is a breakdown of all of the work done by NHPRC <i>"to ensure understanding of our nation's past by promoting, nationwide, the identification, preservation, and dissemination of essential historical documentation."</i> from the Mission Statement.<br>
