	<div class="posts">
	<a name="86714010">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.archives.gov/">NARA | US National Archives & Records Administration</a>.&nbsp; Pretty home page.&nbsp; There are records management initiatives supported by NARA.&nbsp; It would appear that there is much more to study and comprehend with regard to document management and the convergence of document management, record management, content management, and the Web.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#86714010">Monday, December 30, 2002</a></span></div>
