	<a href="http://www.erecordscentral.org/fs_drivingforce.htm">Challenges We All Face With Regard to Electronic Records</a>.&nbsp; A nice summary of what matters here.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#86713694">Monday, December 30, 2002</a></span></div>
