	<div class="posts">
	<a name="86713667">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.erecordscentral.org/index.htm">Global Electronic Records Association</a>.&nbsp; Here is GERA, a non-profit organization with seed funding from CENSA.&nbsp; The interest here is in "Fostering Quality and Excellence in Electronic Records Worldwide."<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#86713667">Monday, December 30, 2002</a></span></div>
<br>
